{"tid":511078,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國將大幅削減對聯合國撥款　指未能有效運作濫用開支","createTime":"2017-12-27T06:13:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-28T07:28:20.000Z","uid":60545,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"90002e31f4dcc7a9e9e5264ca13dc000ab147ddf","tid":511078,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T06:13:15.000Z","msg":"美國駐聯合國代表團宣布，華府將於聯合國2018至19會計年度，大幅削減超過2億8千5百萬美元撥款，亦會削減其他涉及聯合國管理及運作的支援。<br />\n<br />\n美國現時負擔聯合國約22%日常開支。美國駐聯合國代表黑利批評，聯合國未能有效運作，有濫用開支情況，華府在保障美方利益的同時，會繼續尋找提高聯合國運作效率的方法。<br />\n<br />\n聯合國大會上星期就美國承認耶路撒冷是以色列首都，召開緊急會議，通過無約束力決議，指任何宣稱改變耶路撒冷地位的決定和行動都是無效。黑利當時警告表決結果不影響美國，但美國會記著哪些國家投了贊成票。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1371966-20171227.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1371966-20171227.htm&d=hfWUNa6%2FVpXfuI8YhkX16osQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=a07c53df\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1371966-20171227.htm&h=c2106fe2\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1371966-20171227.htm</a>"},{"pid":"0626785aad2ddb27d823c1e13d6f4e7e01fc9b3e","tid":511078,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T05:38:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8046cd17d50097043174aeafbe1b5fd8cc3d211","tid":511078,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T05:39:46.000Z","msg":"由80年代已經屌緊架啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2fd15a76fdb6814eeb9d45c2fa46e310165a3ca","tid":511078,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T05:44:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24c26ea1091c9f249c1e61872b82c452e2f7000f","tid":511078,"uid":4006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor